'''Equipment''' in Dragon Quest III (SNES) includes weapons, armor, shields, and helmets for all classes.

== Equipment by Class ==

=== Hero ===
Can equip most weapon and armor types:
* Swords
* Most armor types
* All shields
* All helmets

=== Warrior (Soldier) ===
* Heavy weapons
* Heavy armor
* All shields
* All helmets

=== Martial Artist (Fighter) ===
* Claws
* Light armor
* Limited shields
* Light helmets

=== Mage (Wizard) ===
* Staffs
* Robes
* No shields
* Light helmets

=== Priest (Pilgrim) ===
* Staffs, maces
* Light-medium armor
* Some shields
* Medium helmets

=== Thief ===
* Daggers
* Light armor
* Some shields
* Light helmets

=== Merchant (Dealer) ===
* Various weapons
* Medium armor
* Some shields
* Medium helmets

=== Sage ===
* Staffs
* Robes and medium armor
* Some shields
* Various helmets

=== Gadabout (Jester) ===
* Limited weapons
* Light armor
* Limited shields
* Various helmets

