== Cursed Equipment ==

Cursed items have high stats but negative effects:
* Cannot be unequipped normally
* Must visit church to remove
* Examples: Armor of Hades, Sword of Destruction

== Orochi Equipment ==

Equipment from the Orochi dungeon:
* Orochi Sword - Powerful weapon
* Found in the snake demon's lair
* Multiple pieces available

== Shop Locations ==

=== Major Equipment Shops ===
* Aliahan - Starting equipment
* Romaly - Mid-game gear
* Isis/Samanao - Later equipment
* Alefgard towns - End-game options

== Equipment Tips ==

'''Class Changing:'''
* Equipment can be unequipped before class change
* New class may not be able to re-equip old items
* Plan equipment around class change strategy

'''Gender Differences:'''
* Some equipment female-only (Sacred Bikini)
* Some equipment male-only
* Consider party composition

'''Personality Effects:'''
* Some items affect personality when equipped
* Personality changes stat growth
* Books also change personality

